{"tid":1570340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足俾popo捉 就打到斷手斷腳先放番出黎 隨時死埋","createTime":"2019-09-15T04:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:40:32.000Z","uid":212255,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd898901f204d5cf9db02493802dd52cbe6c842","tid":1570340,"uid":212255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"手足俾popo捉 就打到斷手斷腳先放番出黎 隨時死埋<br />\n我地捉到藍絲 就打完佢都仲企到響度<br />\n或者佢一扮死我地就放過佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵我地輸啦</span><br />\n<br />\n我軍軍力不斷耗損<br />\n敵軍未真正受傷我地就停手<br />\n人善被人欺<br />\n以後遇到藍絲 唔好當場同佢嘈<br />\n放佢走<br />\n三幾個手足跟佢<br />\n等佢落單再開佢波得唔得<br />\n<br />\n仲有斬人果班<br />\n你地去報牛就係拆左人地間鋪塊玻璃就算？<br />\n咁點對得住俾人斬位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n831有手足死<br />\n叫生要見人 死要見屍叫得咁大聲<br />\n而家叫你郁手打得大力d 都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n運動到而家我方死加重傷幾十人<br />\n對家有冇人死 有冇人重傷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無啊 係無啊 屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你話我聽點贏啊</span>"},{"pid":"0a0743aeb2db4ffcd0dcac9ec665b943eceaa161","tid":1570340,"uid":37722,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"唔好亂咁做比較<br />\n打人 人地在暗 我地在明, 一出錯就輸"},{"pid":"1be31fb3df50f827c847db362ee5d013505f85cd","tid":1570340,"uid":10903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"香港人太善良<br />\n唔好打到人地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">骨折</span>呀"},{"pid":"9be8bcf9d068447bb08c3a5395d4e3a509efbdd0","tid":1570340,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"f32d96ff63eb87702f67ca5edad9a0b1fefaaed7","tid":1570340,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"2點半銅鑼灣東角道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link targ